General.Name: G5 Entertainment AB
General.Description: G5 Entertainment AB (publ) develops and publishes free-to-play games for smartphones, tablets, and personal computers in Sweden. The company's primary portfolio of games includes Hidden City, Jewels of Rome, Sherlock, Jewels of the Wild West, Mahjong Journey, The Secret Society, Jewels of Egypt, Homicide Squad, Sheriff of Mahjong, and Match Town Makeover. It distributes games through Apple App Store, Microsoft Store, Google Play, Amazon Appstore, and Mac App Store, as well as its proprietary store. The company was founded in 2001 and is headquartered in Stockholm, Sweden.
